sources.title: Bunker: Project 12 | Action Sci-Fi | Full Movie
sources.description:
Bunker: Project 12 - The Russians scrap a dangerous scientific project designed to change the course of history. A manhunt ensues after they unsuccessfully attempt to exterminate all the scientists involved in the top secret project.
2016.  Starring - James Cosmo, Joaquín Sánchez, Natasha Alam, Eric Roberts
